# Deploy trigger
#
# The render.yaml buildFilter intentionally ignores packages/web/**, docs/**,
# and **/*.md so content-only commits don't restart the backend. But editorial
# blog posts ARE baked into the backend image at build time (Dockerfile COPYs
# packages/web/src/content/posts, then `build` runs scripts/syncBlogPosts.js),
# so a new/edited post only reaches GET /api/editorial (mobile Home + web) on
# the next backend deploy.
#
# Bump the line below (date + reason) and push to main to force one redeploy.

